Global Compaction Paving Equipment Market Insights
Compaction Paving Equipment Market size was valued at USD 7.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 10.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Compaction Paving Equipment Market Overview
The global compaction paving equipment market is valued at approximately USD 10.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.2% from 2024 to 2032. The market is driven by the increasing demand for efficient and durable paving equipment in infrastructure projects, particularly in developing regions. With construction activities surging across the globe, the demand for compaction paving equipment, including rollers, pavers, and other machinery, is expected to expand rapidly. Market growth is also supported by technological advancements in equipment, automation, and fuel efficiency improvements.

